headline: Make-or-Break Canada Day Weekend Set to Deliver 30%+ Boost for Canada’s Bar and Restaurant Owners
summary: TORONTO, June 18, 2025--The countdown to Canada’s most celebrated summer holiday is on and, for bars and restaurants, this Canada Day long weekend could be a make-or-break moment. According to a new survey commissioned by Square, 72% of Canadians plan to spend more time vacationing in Canada and enjoying local restaurants this year—an increase attributed to the current political climate.
